name: HMS Plymouth (Azur Lane)
description:
Updated Mar/4/2023:

After a week's futile struggle with the Lion optimizer, I turned to more efficient methods such as the D-Adaption; hence the remastered 2.0 and 2.1 versions are no longer overfitted, more compatible across different checkpoints and make up only half the original file size without degrading her details.

Features HMS Plymouth from Azur Lane in her original costume & Heart-Throbbing Refreshment bikini costume, trained on ACertainModel with good level of flexibility.

Release v1: applying with a high weight (0.7-0.9) is recommended, going below will noticeably impact character robustness.

Release v2.0 & 2.1: Works well up to 1.0 full weight.

Prompts

(Note that v2.0 & 2.1 takes plmtazln as trigger for her face & hairstyles)

  • Base: white dress, bare shoulders, half gloves, high heels, blunt bangs

  • Swimsuit: bikini, hair ribbon, twintails, blunt bangs

modelVersions.name: Release v2.1
modelVersions.description:
Further trained on v2.0 basis, with much more stable costume details.

FP16, dataset size 60 pics
